title: Behind the Scenes Minis: Annie and Rinderpest
itunes:title: Behind the Scenes Minis: Annie and Rinderpest
description:
Holly and Tracy talk about Annie Londonderry's cavalier relationship with the truth and the challenges of travel with the wrong clothes and bike. Then talk turns to a strange paper that Tracy read while researching rinderpest.
